When the paper was given to the AI model o1 from OpenAI, it was able to spot the error. What other errors might be hidden in the tens of millions of published research papers? What mistakes have gone unnoticed? What if an AI went and found all the erorrs?

Ink Finance allows a one-stop and frictionless solution for organized financial activities, with scalability and customizability.
